title: Justin Bieber & Ruby Rose Have Another Look-Alike Moment (Video)
text: Justin Bieber steps out for a night with friends after the 2015 MTV EMAs on Sunday evening (October 25) in Milan, Italy. During the awards show, the 21-year-old singer shared a funny moment with host Ruby Rose .
